  <div class="xhr_comment_body">
    <a style="font-weight:bold" href="/user/show/109200206-keahna">Keahna</a>

      
<span id="freeTextContainer17351202559316674499">As a high schooler, I’m quite surprised at how little people think of 15 year olds grasp on mental health and ability to comprehend such intense issue</span>
  <span id="freeText17351202559316674499" style="display:none">As a high schooler, I’m quite surprised at how little people think of 15 year olds grasp on mental health and ability to comprehend such intense issues. I was a sophomore/junior at the age of 15, and I know for a fact that most people that age that I was around had a strong understanding of mental health issues because we had started experiencing that around the age of 11-12, but that may just be who I ended up being friends with and my own personal experience</span>
  <a data-text-id="17351202559316674499" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

