      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/12898.Stephen_Chbosky">About Stephen Chbosky</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/12898.Stephen_Chbosky"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1599132962p3/12898.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/12898.Stephen_Chbosky">Stephen Chbosky
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
11,420
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer12726213159054576562">Stephen Chbosky grew up in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, and graduated from the University of Southern California&apos;s Filmic Writing Program. His first film, The Four Corners of Nowhere, premiered at the 1995 Sundance Film Festival and went on to win Best Narrative Feature honors at the Chicago Underground Film Festival. <br/><br/>He is the recipient of the Abraham Polonsky Screenwriting Award for his screenplay </span>
  <span id="freeText12726213159054576562" style="display:none">Stephen Chbosky grew up in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, and graduated from the University of Southern California's Filmic Writing Program. His first film, The Four Corners of Nowhere, premiered at the 1995 Sundance Film Festival and went on to win Best Narrative Feature honors at the Chicago Underground Film Festival. <br /><br />He is the recipient of the Abraham Polonsky Screenwriting Award for his screenplay Everything Divided as well as a participant in the Sundance Institute's filmmakers' lab for his current project, Fingernails and Smooth Skin. Chbosky lives in New York. <br /><br />For more information, please see <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_Chbosky">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_...</a><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="12726213159054576562" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="bigBoxBottom"></div></div>

  

